title: Rocksmith Crack (By Themperror and Sam2k8) CRACK ONLY
description:
Here is the crack for Rocksmith (Finally)

you DO need the cable to play this game though..

Thank Sam2k5/sam2k8 for the crack and me for delivering all the needed files to him :P

This crack should work with the other torrents for rocksmith that I have uploaded,

(The retail DVD won't work as you'll need to install it then)

so you'll need this:
 <a href="
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7745402/Rocksmith_Installed_Steam_Files" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7745402/Rocksmith_Installed_Steam_Files</a> (which seems to have a corrupted file in it (sorry))

or this:
 <a href="
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7745439/Rocksmith_PC_Steam_Backup_Files" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7745439/Rocksmith_PC_Steam_Backup_Files</a>


Copy paste all the files over in the directory where the .exe is

(SteamsteamappscommonRocksmith)

and edit the LumaEmu.ini 
so that this line:


[SteamClient]
# Set path to steamclient.dll (not the original)
SteamClientDll = C:steamclient.dll

points to the path where you have the steamclient.dll (Which is included in the rar)

(do not point it to the original dll, it won't work)
